# start mointer mode, we can capture the wireless packet at the difference channel

two methods

one :
				iwconfig wlan0 up

				open up it ,we need to appoint one channel that we want to capture
				iwconfig wlan0mon channel 11

two:
				airmon-ng start wlan0

				we can use the tool to scan the environment to find kind of channel
				
				airodump-ng wlan0mon



